{"tid":1082362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵相撞】2次事故撥3,500萬回饋乘客 5月11至13日推約半價優惠","createTime":"2019-03-29T02:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T04:18:25.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ee87a2257988d9ab3a6285833bedd10a0754d1","tid":1082362,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/13FpWJd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F13FpWJd.png&h=c1e062ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵本月18日凌晨有兩列無載客列車在中環站隧道內相撞，導致中環至金鐘的列車服務要停駛兩日進行搶修。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep74chg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp74chg.png&h=a88a8ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉天成（左）宣佈港鐵5月11日至13日將向乘客提供大約半價的車票優惠。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3MgNQK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3MgNQK.png&h=a0017080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳帆稱在找出列車相撞肇因前，已勒令港鐵暫停測試新訊號系統。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n港鐵兩列列車於本月18日凌晨在中環站隧道內相撞事故，令荃灣綫中環站至金鐘站的服務要暫停兩日搶修。立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會今早召開會議討論事故，港鐵車務總監劉天成表示，港鐵將會於5月11日（周六）、5月12日（周日）及5月13日（周一）推岀大約半價的車票優惠，預料1,300萬人受惠。<br />\n<br />\n劉天成指就今次列車相撞事故，會按票價調整機制中的「服務表現安排」撥出上限2,500萬元，在明年票價調整時回饋乘客，港鐵亦已決定5月11至13日一連3日向乘客提供大約半價的車票優惠。另外，港鐵亦會就日前機場快綫架空電纜故障事件撥出1,000萬元，同樣用於明年調整時回饋乘客。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長陳帆重申，港鐵在事故中責無旁貸，港鐵已成立調查委員會，料3個月內會有報告，而機電署亦另設獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆稱，機電署已監督港鐵再次抽驗現有訊號系統，包括今次失靈的連鎖功能系統及列車保護系統。港鐵現時已暫停測試新訊號系統，直至確認今次事故原因和作出改正後，政府才會容許恢復測試。"},{"pid":"35bbf5855c183c38401f1582dc51f7f531f34684","tid":1082362,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"又星期六日？ 我屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"ded97d3060c7b95db8eb9aa9f32e968d0d2a56bc","tid":1082362,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"買月票點計"},{"pid":"876e617bc0b04262532b04f8b2ddba6fb3c96d01","tid":1082362,"uid":70336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:41:06.000Z","msg":"壞就壞平日，補就補假期。<br />\ndllm"},{"pid":"57dbebb2a1480ddcf184d91e624944f6b780f3c3","tid":1082362,"uid":27287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩<br />\n又星期六日<br />\n逼鳩我星期六日又要坐你老母狗鐵呀冚家產"},{"pid":"da5414064fcc02b240fe4ed03b966d2a11db3a60","tid":1082362,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"多撚謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdd5779a647eec22d0a6cdc4f75e17d0830c3b2","tid":1082362,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"多撚謝"},{"pid":"f060f35684d71ac1b9378850f9f15360702f3dcf","tid":1082362,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5414064fcc02b240fe4ed03b966d2a11db3a60","tid":1082362,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"多撚謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176a346bb414ce1267fafbd3486110cc6d0b5154","tid":1082362,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:12:59.000Z","msg":"祝港鐵高層畀車撞死。"},{"pid":"853989c8cb971531b00bb750c1d40d5224e10f4b","tid":1082362,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}